OL,5, Actress, screenwriter and director Kay 
OL,6, Mellor has died aged 71, it has been   
OL,7, announced.                             
OL,9,FA spokesman for her TV production      
OL,10,Fcompany, Rollem Productions, confirmed 
OL,11,F"with profound sadness" that she died  
OL,12,Fon Sunday.                             
OL,14,FShe was known for creating and writing 
OL,15,Fthe ITV series Fat Friends - which     
OL,16,Fhelped launch James Corden's career.   
OL,18,FMellor also wrote comedy and drama     
OL,19,Fseries such as The Syndicate,          
OL,20,FGirlfriends and Band of Gold.          
